I had an amazing Easter at the happiest place on earth with the people I love most! The Easter character brunch at Storytellers cafe was so amazing! The food was yummy drinks were great and the characters spent so much time with the boys at our table and the servers were extremely friendly and on top of everything. Then we did an Easter egg hunt at California Adventure to find 12 hidden eggs throughout the park for a surprise at the end! We spent the rest of the day going on a ton of rides and ate some yummy snacks like pretzels corn dogs and churros! It was some much needed fun and one of the best days I have had in a long time. I highly recommend Easter at Disney and I think this is a new tradition for us! I hope everyone else had a beautiful and blessed Easter! #easter #disney #disneyland #happy #love #blessed #family

This is a picture of delta dreamflight. This was an omnimover dark ride located in tomorrowland. It opened on June 23 1989. The guest entered a room similar to the haunted mansion with the blue cars that they say on. Then they went through scenes depicting the history of flight. This attraction was sponsored by delta airlines. Delta ended the sponsorship in 1995 and the ride was renamed take flight and all of the delta references were gone. But in June 1996 it closed its doors to be replaced by buzz light years space ranger spin. +Have you ever been on delta dreamflight+{ #waltdisneyworldresort #waltdisney #rivercountry #abandoned #waterpark #baylake #fortwilderness #retrodisney #disneywaterpark #disneypool #disneywaterslide #extinctwaltdisneyworld #orlando #florida #igfamous #sad #throwback #mystery #outdated #disney #dancemoms #craniumcommand #toontown #testtrack @rivercountrywaterpark }

Pirates of the Caribbean~Pirates of the Caribbean is one of the most popular attractions at the Disneyland park. The boat travels at a low speed (excluding the drops) causing the ride to last around 16 minutes. The ride also has a resturant attached called the Blue Bayou where you can eat by the water as the ride goes by in a dark setting with the only light source being candle light.
